Title: Christopher Martin
Name: Christopher Martin
Bio: Christopher is an investment analyst at the firm, supporting the team in due diligence and market research. He has a background in economics and finance, and has worked with several startups in the consumer goods space. Christopher holds a BS in Economics from University of California, Berkeley and an MS in Finance from Columbia Business School. Christopher is an avid reader and enjoys playing the guitar in his free time.

Title: Alex Harrison
Name: Alex Harrison
Bio: Alex is a partner at the firm, leading investments in enterprise software and cybersecurity. She has over 15 years of experience in the tech industry, and has worked with several successful startups and public companies. Alex holds a BS in Computer Science from University of Texas at Austin and an MBA from Harvard Business School. Alex is a sought-after speaker on enterprise software and cybersecurity and has published several articles on these topics.

Title: Matthew Sullivan
Name: Matthew Sullivan
Bio: Matthew is an associate at the firm, supporting the investment team in sourcing and evaluating new opportunities. He has a background in finance and accounting, and has worked with several startups in the fintech space. Matthew holds a BS in Business Administration from University of Southern California and an MBA from UCLA Anderson School of Management. Matthew is an avid traveler and enjoys trying new foods and drinks.

Title: Elizabeth Green
Name: Elizabeth Green
Bio: Elizabeth is a venture partner at the firm, bringing her expertise in healthcare and life sciences to the table. She is a medical doctor with over 15 years of experience in the industry, and has founded and advised several successful healthcare startups. Elizabeth holds an MD from Harvard Medical School and an MBA from Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania. Elizabeth is a sought-after speaker on healthcare innovation and has published several papers on medical device innovation and digital health.

Title: Ryan Jenkins
Name: Ryan Jenkins
Bio: Ryan is a principal at the firm, focusing on investments in artificial intelligence, machine learning, and data analytics. He has a background in engineering and computer science, and has worked with several successful startups in the past. Ryan holds a BS in Computer Science from Carnegie Mellon University and an MS in Engineering from Stanford University. Ryan is an avid reader and enjoys hiking and rock climbing in his free time.

Title: Emily Wilson
Name: Emily Wilson
Bio: Emily is a seasoned venture capitalist with over 10 years of experience investing in early-stage tech companies. She has a strong track record of identifying and supporting successful startups, and has played a key role in shaping the firm's investment strategy. Emily holds an MBA from Stanford Graduate School of Business and a BS in Computer Science from MIT. Outside of work, Emily is passionate about promoting diversity and inclusion in the tech industry and serves on the board of several non-profit organizations.
